replies.author: 秋灯Lantern
replies.txt_content:
本帖最后由 秋灯Lantern 于 2020-1-31 00:52 编辑 

hmmm

Caused by: slimeknights.tconstruct.library.TinkerAPIException: [TCon API] Could not register Material "osmium": It was already registered by Moar Tinkers复制代码
这一段 是匠魂[tconstruct 全拼Tinkers' Construct ]要注册一个叫"osmium"的东西 

但是Moar Tinkers[更多材料]这个mod也有这个东西 所以冲突了
二者取其一就好了

你试试 没问题的话就最佳呗~

replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content:
.minecraft\config\pewter\pewter.cfg

中，设置

"material blacklist:" {
    # Blacklist for Pewter Materials. Add the materials you don't want and they will not be loaded on startup [default: ]
    S:materialBlacklist <
    osmium
     >
}


无需删除 mod
